/* 设计基座：取材自麻将桌 —— 毡绿（桌面）、象牙白（牌面）、朱红（立直棒红点）、琥珀（庄家标志） */
page {
  --felt: #0f5342;
  --felt-deep: #0a3d31;
  --felt-bright: #1a7a5e;
  --ivory: #fbf8ef;
  --ivory-deep: #f3edda;
  --ivory-edge: #e3dcc4;
  --ink: #1f2b27;
  --red: #b93a28;
  --amber: #b8862c;
  --muted: #6e7b76;
  --line: #e9e4d3;
  --bg: #f1eee3;

  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
}

.page {
  min-height: 100vh;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 32rpx;
}

.section {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
}

.panel {
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1rpx solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 20rpx;
  padding: 30rpx;
  box-shadow: 0 2rpx 10rpx rgba(31, 43, 39, 0.04);
}

.label {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 12rpx;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 26rpx;
}

.input {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 88rpx;
  padding: 0 24rpx;
  border: 1rpx solid var(--ivory-edge);
  border-radius: 14rpx;
  background: #fdfcf8;
  color: var(--ink);
  font-size: 30rpx;
}

.button-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 18rpx;
  align-items: center;
}

/* 统一按钮体系：清除微信默认边框与半宽居中行为 */
button::after {
  border: none;
}

.primary-button,
.secondary-button,
.ghost-button,
.danger-button {
  width: 100% !important;
  min-height: 92rpx;
  margin: 0;
  border-radius: 16rpx;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 92rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.button-row .primary-button,
.button-row .secondary-button,
.button-row .ghost-button,
.button-row .danger-button {
  flex: 1;
  width: auto !important;
}

.primary-button {
  background: var(--felt);
  color: var(--ivory);
}

.primary-button:active {
  background: var(--felt-deep);
}

.secondary-button {
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 2rpx solid var(--felt);
  color: var(--felt);
  line-height: 88rpx;
}

.secondary-button:active {
  background: #eef4f0;
}

.ghost-button {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2rpx solid var(--ivory-edge);
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 88rpx;
}

.danger-button {
  background: var(--red);
  color: #ffffff;
}

/* 小尺寸行内按钮（区块标题右侧的操作） */
.mini-button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  width: fit-content !important;
  min-width: 0;
  min-height: 60rpx;
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 28rpx;
  border-radius: 30rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid var(--felt);
  background: #ffffff;
  color: var(--felt);
  font-size: 25rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 56rpx;
}

.num {
  font-feature-settings: "tnum";
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
}

.muted {
  color: var(--muted);
}

.empty {
  padding: 36rpx 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 27rpx;
}
